        "management": "Neoadjuvant chemotherapy (anthracycline + taxane). Surgery. Radiotherapy. PARP inhibitors for BRCA carriers. Immunotherapy (Pembrolizumab) for PD-L1 positive."
      },
      {
        "id": "inflammatory_breast_cancer",
